          BRANCH    EXIT,AWRD9999
.
          CALL      CLEA0000
          PACK      KEY3,SP3                 * add inpatients on previous day
          CALL      RDSSECT3                 * read the 3rd tempfile
AWRD6000  CALL      RDKSECT3
          BRANCH    OVRCD,AWRD7000
.
          MATCH     XWARD,CWARD
